240 prepareSpecializationLayer(pageType='main'){
241 const data = this.state.alumniData.specializationData;
242 var otherManagementFlag = false;
243 var lastIndex = '';
244 var self = this;
245 const listItems = new Array();
246 for(var index in data){
247 var splz = data[index];
248 var specializationName = '';
249 if( splz.name== "Systems" || splz.name == "#N/A") {
250 specializationName = '';
251 }
252 else if(splz.name == "Other Management") {
253 otherManagementFlag = true;
254 specializationName = '';
255 }
256 else if(splz.name == "Marketing") {
257 specializationName = 'Sales & Marketing';
258 }else if(splz.name == "HR/Industrial Relations"){
259 specializationName = 'Human Resources';
260 }else if(splz.name == "Information Technology"){
261 specializationName = 'IT';
262 }else{
263 specializationName = splz.name;
264 }
265 lastIndex = index;
266 if(specializationName){
267 listItems.push(<li key={index} onClick={self.activeSpecialization.bind(self,specializationName,splz.name, pageType)}>
268 {specializationName}
269 </li>);
270 }
271 }
272
273 return(<ul className="ul-list" key="ullist">
274 <li key='all' onClick={self.activeSpecialization.bind(self,'All Specialization','All', pageType)}>All Specialization</li>
275 {listItems}
276 {(otherManagementFlag)?<li key={lastIndex+1} onClick={self.activeSpecialization.bind(self,'Other Management','Other Management', pageType)}>Other Management</li>:''}
277 </ul>);
278 }

173 scrollToY(scrollTargetY, speed, easing) {
Warning Row 174, Column 2: "Mixed spaces and tabs." no-mixed-spaces-and-tabs
174 // scrollTargetY: the target scrollY property of the window
Warning Row 175, Column 2: "Mixed spaces and tabs." no-mixed-spaces-and-tabs
175 // speed: time in pixels per second
Warning Row 176, Column 2: "Mixed spaces and tabs." no-mixed-spaces-and-tabs
176 // easing: easing equation to use
177
Warning Row 178, Column 2: "Mixed spaces and tabs." no-mixed-spaces-and-tabs
178 var scrollY = window.scrollY,
Warning Row 179, Column 2: "Mixed spaces and tabs." no-mixed-spaces-and-tabs
Error Row 179, Column 10: "'scrollTargetY' is already defined." no-redeclare
179 scrollTargetY = scrollTargetY || 0,
Warning Row 180, Column 2: "Mixed spaces and tabs." no-mixed-spaces-and-tabs
Error Row 180, Column 10: "'speed' is already defined." no-redeclare
180 speed = speed || 2000,
Warning Row 181, Column 2: "Mixed spaces and tabs." no-mixed-spaces-and-tabs
Error Row 181, Column 10: "'easing' is already defined." no-redeclare
181 easing = easing || 'easeOutSine',
Warning Row 182, Column 2: "Mixed spaces and tabs." no-mixed-spaces-and-tabs
182 currentTime = 0;
183
Warning Row 184, Column 2: "Mixed spaces and tabs." no-mixed-spaces-and-tabs
184 // min time .1, max time .8 seconds
Warning Row 185, Column 2: "Mixed spaces and tabs." no-mixed-spaces-and-tabs
185 var time = Math.max(.1, Math.min(Math.abs(scrollY - scrollTargetY) / speed, .8));
186
Warning Row 187, Column 2: "Mixed spaces and tabs." no-mixed-spaces-and-tabs
187 // easing equations from https://github.com/danro/easing-js/blob/master/easing.js
Warning Row 188, Column 2: "Mixed spaces and tabs." no-mixed-spaces-and-tabs
Error Row 188, Column 10: "'PI_D2' is assigned a value but never used." no-unused-vars
188 var PI_D2 = Math.PI / 2,
189 easingEquations = {
190 easeOutSine: function (pos) {
191 return Math.sin(pos * (Math.PI / 2));
192 },
193 easeInOutSine: function (pos) {
194 return (-0.5 * (Math.cos(Math.PI * pos) - 1));
195 },
196 easeInOutQuint: function (pos) {
197 if ((pos /= 0.5) < 1) {
198 return 0.5 * Math.pow(pos, 5);
199 }
200 return 0.5 * (Math.pow((pos - 2), 5) + 2);
201 }
202 };

571 renderFeeValue()
572 {
573 const {data, isAmp} = this.props;
574 let feeValue = data.currentLocation.fees != null ? data.currentLocation.fees : null;
575 let tooltip = false;
576 let showDisclaimer = false;
577 if(feeValue == null)
578 {
579 feeValue = data.courseFees!= null && data.courseFees.feesUnitName != null && typeof data.courseFees.feesUnitName != 'undefined' ? data.courseFees.feesUnitName+' ' : '';
580 feeValue = data.courseFees != null && data.courseFees.fees != null && typeof data.courseFees.fees.totalFees.general != 'undefined' ? feeValue +''+getRupeesDisplayableAmount(data.courseFees.fees.totalFees.general.value) : '';
581 if(data.courseFees != null && data.courseFees.fees != null && typeof data.courseFees.fees.totalFees != 'undefined' && Object.keys(data.courseFees.fees.totalFees).length > 1)
582 tooltip = true;
583 if( data.courseFees != null && typeof data.courseFees.fees != 'undefined' && data.courseFees.fees != null && data.courseFees != null && typeof data.courseFees.fees != 'undefined' && data.courseFees.fees != null && typeof data.courseFees.fees.showDisclaimer != 'undefined' && data.courseFees.fees.showDisclaimer)
Warning Row 584, Column 2: "Mixed spaces and tabs." no-mixed-spaces-and-tabs
584 {
Warning Row 585, Column 2: "Mixed spaces and tabs." no-mixed-spaces-and-tabs
585 showDisclaimer = true;
Warning Row 586, Column 2: "Mixed spaces and tabs." no-mixed-spaces-and-tabs
586 }
587 }
588 else
589 {
590 var clFees = (typeof data.currentLocation.fees != 'undefined') ? data.currentLocation.fees : {};
591 for(var clfKey in clFees)
592 {
Warning Row 593, Column 2: "Mixed spaces and tabs." no-mixed-spaces-and-tabs
593 if(clFees[clfKey]['category'] == 'general')
Warning Row 594, Column 2: "Mixed spaces and tabs." no-mixed-spaces-and-tabs
594 {
Warning Row 595, Column 2: "Mixed spaces and tabs." no-mixed-spaces-and-tabs
595 feeValue = clFees[clfKey]['fees_unit_name']+ " "+getRupeesDisplayableAmount(clFees[clfKey]['fees_value']);
Warning Row 596, Column 2: "Mixed spaces and tabs." no-mixed-spaces-and-tabs
596 }
Warning Row 597, Column 2: "Mixed spaces and tabs." no-mixed-spaces-and-tabs
597 }
598 if(Object.keys(clFees).length > 1)
599 {
Warning Row 600, Column 2: "Mixed spaces and tabs." no-mixed-spaces-and-tabs
600 tooltip = true;
601 }
Warning Row 602, Column 2: "Mixed spaces and tabs." no-mixed-spaces-and-tabs
602 var listing_location_id = typeof data.currentLocation['listing_location_id'] != 'undefined' ? data.currentLocation['listing_location_id'] : '';
603
604 if(listing_location_id != '')
605 {
Warning Row 606, Column 2: "Mixed spaces and tabs." no-mixed-spaces-and-tabs
606 showDisclaimer = data.courseFees != null && data.courseFees.locationWiseFees != null && typeof data.courseFees.locationWiseFees[listing_location_id] != 'undefined' ? data.courseFees.locationWiseFees[listing_location_id].showDisclaimer : false;
607 }
608 }
609 let feesTooltipHtml = [];
610 if(tooltip)
611 {
612 if(isAmp){
613 feesTooltipHtml.push(<li key="1" className='f12 color-6 m-5btm'>{data.tooltipData.feesTooltip}</li>);
614 }else{
615 feesTooltipHtml.push(<p key="2">{data.tooltipData.feesTooltip}</p>);
616 }
617 }
618 if(showDisclaimer)
619 {
620
621 if(isAmp){
Warning Row 622, Column 2: "Mixed spaces and tabs." no-mixed-spaces-and-tabs
622 feesTooltipHtml.push(<li key="5" className='f12 color-6 m-5btm'>{data.tooltipData.feesDisclaimer}</li>);
623 }else {
624 feesTooltipHtml.push(<br key="3"/>);
625 feesTooltipHtml.push(<br key="4"/>);
626 feesTooltipHtml.push(<p key="6">{data.tooltipData.feesDisclaimer}</p>);
627 }
628 }
629
630 if(feeValue != null && feeValue != '')
631 {
632 return (
Warning Row 633, Column 2: "Mixed spaces and tabs." no-mixed-spaces-and-tabs
633 <React.Fragment key="fee-main">
634 {(isAmp) ? <React.Fragment>
Warning Row 635, Column 2: "Mixed spaces and tabs." no-mixed-spaces-and-tabs
635 <p className="pos-rl color-9 f12 "> Total Fees {typeof data.tooltipData.feesTooltip != 'undefined' && tooltip && <a className='pos-rl' on='tap:fee-more-data'><i className='cmn-sprite clg-info i-block v-mdl'></i></a>}</p>
Warning Row 636, Column 2: "Mixed spaces and tabs." no-mixed-spaces-and-tabs
636 <span className='block color-3 f13 font-w6'>{feeValue}</span>
Warning Row 637, Column 2: "Mixed spaces and tabs." no-mixed-spaces-and-tabs
637 {typeof data.tooltipData.feesTooltip != 'undefined' && tooltip && <AmpLightBox onRef={ref => (this.feeLayer = ref)} data={feesTooltipHtml} heading="Total Fees" id="fee-more-data" datatype={"addul"}/>}
Warning Row 638, Column 2: "Mixed spaces and tabs." no-mixed-spaces-and-tabs
638 </React.Fragment> : <React.Fragment>
639 <p><span className='clg-label-tip'>Total Fees {typeof data.tooltipData.feesTooltip != 'undefined' && tooltip && <i className='info-icon' onClick={this.openFeesLayer}></i>}</span></p>
640 <span>{feeValue}</span>
641 {typeof data.tooltipData.feesTooltip != 'undefined' && tooltip && <PopupLayer onRef={ref => (this.feeLayer = ref)} data={feesTooltipHtml} heading="Total Fees"/>}
Warning Row 642, Column 2: "Mixed spaces and tabs." no-mixed-spaces-and-tabs
642 </React.Fragment>
643 }
644
Warning Row 645, Column 2: "Mixed spaces and tabs." no-mixed-spaces-and-tabs
645 </React.Fragment>
Warning Row 646, Column 2: "Mixed spaces and tabs." no-mixed-spaces-and-tabs

649 renderMediumHtml()
650 {
651 const {data, isAmp} = this.props;
652 var showCount = false;
653 let mediumInstruction = typeof data.mediumOfInstruction != 'undefined' && data.mediumOfInstruction != null ? data.mediumOfInstruction : [];
654 if(mediumInstruction.length == 0)
655 return;
656 showCount = mediumInstruction.length > 1 ? true : false;
657 var mediumName = mediumInstruction[0].name;
658 var mediumHtml = [];
659 if(mediumName && mediumName != 'English' || showCount)
660 {
661 if(isAmp){
662 mediumHtml.push(<p key='medium' className='color-9 pos-rl f12'>Medium<span className='block color-3 f12 font-w6'>{mediumName} </span></p>);
663 mediumHtml.push(<span key='medium-name'>{showCount && <React.Fragment key="frg-medium"><a className='block color-b f12 font-w6 ga-analytic' on='tap:medium-more-data' data-vars-event-name="MEDIUM_MORE"> +{mediumInstruction.length-1} more</a>
664 <AmpLightBox onRef={ref => (this.mediumLayer = ref)} data={this.generateMediumLayer()} heading="Mediums of Education" id="medium-more-data"/></React.Fragment>}</span>);
665 }else{
666 mediumHtml.push(<p key='medium'><span className='clg-label-tip'>Medium</span></p>);
667 mediumHtml.push(<span key='medium-name'>{mediumName} {showCount && <React.Fragment key="frg-medium"><a className='clp-mrLink' href='javascript:void(0);' onClick={this.openMediumLayer}> +{mediumInstruction.length-1} more</a>
668 <PopupLayer onRef={ref => (this.mediumLayer = ref)} data={this.generateMediumLayer()} heading="Mediums of Education"/></React.Fragment>}</span>);
669 }
670 }
671 return mediumHtml;
672 }
